  "title": "Full time/Locum Dentists",
  "description": "<p>Passionate about dental care?</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>With three conveniently located clinics in Ang Mo Kio, Bedok, and Orchard, <strong>WeSmile Dental Care</strong> is your trusted partner in oral health. We are dedicated to delivering dental excellence for your everyday care, with a mission to inspire confidence and create healthy smiles that enhance your quality of life.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>With a team of dedicated and experienced dentists, we offer a comprehensive range of preventative, restorative and aesthetic dental services — from scaling and polishing, dental implants, root canal treatments, teeth aligner, veneers and more.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you are registered with the Singapore Dental Council and hold a valid practicing certificate, we'd love to share more about our opportunities. Dental officers who are in the final year of bond are welcome to apply as well.</p>",
